"title": "2366: Jesus Christ, prophecies concerning",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2366: jesus christ, prophecies concerning",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The OT points ahead to the person and ministry of Jesus Christ. Christ's fulfilment of OT prophecy is often noted by NT writers as a demonstration of God's faithfulness to his promises of salvation and as confirmation of the divine authority of Jesus Christ.</p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ fulfils OT prophecy</h2>\n<h3>He fulfils the OT as a whole</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:27\">LUK 24:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:17\">MAT 5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:44\">LUK 24:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:20\">2CO 1:20</a></p>\n<h3>He fulfils God's promises to Abraham</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:14\">GAL 3:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:54-Luke1:55\">LUK 1:54–1:55</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:72-Luke1:74\">LUK 1:72–1:74</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:16\">GAL 3:16</a></p>\n<h3>He fulfils God's promises through the prophets</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:43\">ACT 10:43</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:56\">MAT 26:56</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:18\">ACT 3:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:24\">ACT 3:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:27\">ACT 13:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:2\">ROM 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:10\">1PE 1:10</a></p>\n<h2>Prophecies about Jesus Christ's birth</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:23\">MAT 1:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:14\">ISA 7:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:21\">MAT 1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:31-Luke1:32\">LUK 1:31–1:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:6\">ISA 9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:6-Matt2:7\">MAT 2:6–2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic5:2\">MIC 5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:15\">MAT 2:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:1\">HOS 11:1</a></p>\n<h2>Prophecies about Jesus Christ's ministry</h2>\n<h3>He brings good news</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:17-Luke4:19\">LUK 4:17–4:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1-Isa61:2\">ISA 61:1–61:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:13-Matt4:16\">MAT 4:13–4:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:1-Isa9:2\">ISA 9:1–9:2</a></p>\n<h3>He divides people and is rejected</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:34-Luke2:35\">LUK 2:34–2:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:11-Matt3:12\">MAT 3:11–3:12</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:7-Mark1:8\">MRK 1:7–1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:16-Luke3:17\">LUK 3:16–3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:42\">MAT 21:42</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:10-Mark12:11\">MRK 12:10–12:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:17\">LUK 20:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:22-Ps118:23\">PSA 118:22–118:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:18\">JHN 13:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps41:9\">PSA 41:9</a></p>\n<h3>He teaches in parables</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:35\">MAT 13:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:2\">PSA 78:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:13-Matt13:15\">MAT 13:13–13:15</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:11-Mark4:12\">MRK 4:11–4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:10\">LUK 8:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:9-Isa6:10\">ISA 6:9–6:10</a></p>\n<h2>Prophecies about Jesus Christ's death</h2>\n<h3>The Lord's Supper</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:28\">MAT 26:28</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:24\">MRK 14:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:20\">LUK 22:20</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:12\">ISA 53:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:34\">JER 31:34</a></p>\n<h3>The betrayal</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:9-Matt27:10\">MAT 27:9–27:10</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer19:1-Jer19:13\">JER 19:1–19:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech11:12-Zech11:13\">ZEC 11:12–11:13</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:9\">JHN 18:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:39\">JHN 6:39</a></p>\n<h3>The cross</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:46\">MAT 27:46</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:34\">MRK 15:34</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:1\">PSA 22:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:35\">MAT 27:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:18\">PSA 22:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:46\">LUK 23:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:5\">PSA 31:5</a></p>\n<h2>Prophecies about Jesus Christ's resurrection and ascension</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:39-Matt12:40\">MAT 12:39–12:40</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:29-Luke11:30\">LUK 11:29–11:30</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah1:17\">JON 1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:25-Acts2:28\">ACT 2:25–2:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:8-Ps16:11\">PSA 16:8–16:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:31\">ACT 2:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:35\">ACT 13:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:34\">ACT 2:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps110:1\">PSA 110:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:8\">EPH 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:18\">PSA 68:18</a></p>\n<h2>Prophecies about Jesus Christ's titles</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ as Son of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:32-Acts13:33\">ACT 13:32–13:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:7\">PSA 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:5\">HEB 1:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:5\">HEB 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:44\">MAT 22:44</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:36\">MRK 12:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:42\">LUK 20:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps110:1\">PSA 110:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:8-Heb1:9\">HEB 1:8–1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:6-Ps45:7\">PSA 45:6–45:7</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ as Son of Man</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:64\">MAT 26:64</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:62\">MRK 14:62</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:69\">LUK 22:69</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:13-Dan7:14\">DAN 7:13–7:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:31\">MRK 8:31</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:22\">LUK 9:22</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ as Son of David</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:16\">REV 22:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:12-2Sam7:16\">2SA 7:12–7:16</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr17:11-1Chr17:14\">1CH 17:11–17:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:32-Luke1:33\">LUK 1:32–1:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:7\">ISA 9:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:34\">ACT 13:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:3\">ISA 55:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:12\">ROM 15:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:1\">ISA 11:1</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ as the coming Messianic king</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:31\">MAT 26:31</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:27\">MRK 14:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech13:7\">ZEC 13:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:4-Matt21:5\">MAT 21:4–21:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:9\">ZEC 9:9</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ as the suffering servant</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:32-Acts8:35\">ACT 8:32–8:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:7-Isa53:8\">ISA 53:7–53:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:17-Matt12:21\">MAT 12:17–12:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:1-Isa42:4\">ISA 42:1–42:4</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ as the prophet who is to come</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:22\">ACT 3:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut18:18\">DEU 18:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:18-Luke4:19\">LUK 4:18–4:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1-Isa61:2\">ISA 61:1–61:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:14\">JHN 6:14</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ as priest</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:21\">HEB 7:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps110:4\">PSA 110:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:5-Heb5:6\">HEB 5:5–5:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:17\">HEB 7:17</a></p>",
